onseSchema` through it so schema-descent checks see the inner `data` payload. Required because the `/flip-you/verify/{pda}` 200 body is now an envelope `oneOf`; the existing `resolveSchema` only unwrapped `allOf` / `anyOf`.\n235\t  - Updated `backend/src/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts` FlipYou suites:\n236\t    - `POST /flipyou/create` 200 test: destructures `body.data`, asserts `body.ok === true`; commitment length check moved onto `data.commitment`.\n237\t    - `POST /flipyou/create` 401 tests (missing / expired JWT): assert `body.ok === false` and `body.error.code === \"AUTH_REQUIRED\"`.\n238\t    - `POST /flipyou/create` 403 test: asserts `body.error.code === \"FORBIDDEN\"`.\n239\t    - `POST /flipyou/create` 409 collision test: asserts envelope shape, `error.code === \"CONFLICT\"`, preserved human-readable message.\n240\t    - Both rate-limit tests: assert `body.error.code === \"RATE_LIMITED\"`.\n241\t    - `GET /flipyou/verify/:pda` and `/by-id/:matchId` success tests: destructure `body.data`.\n242\t    - `GET /flipyou/by-id/:matchId` 404 test: asserts `error.code === \"MATCH_NOT_FOUND\"`.\n243\t    - `GET /flipyou/history`: asserts envelope `body.data.rounds === []`.\n244\t    - `POST /pot-shot/create` + verify/by-id for pot-shot left unchanged (pot-shot routes convert in iteration 12).\n245\t- **Verification**:\n246\t  - `pnpm -C backend typecheck:self` → exit 0\n247\t  - `pnpm -C backend lint:self` → exit 0\n248\t  - Targeted: `vitest run --config vitest.unit.config.ts src/__tests__/openapi-contract.test.ts` → 8/8 passed\n249\t  - Targeted: `vitest run --config vitest.integration.config.ts src/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts` → 14/14 passed\n250\t  - Targeted: `vitest run --config vitest.unit.config.ts src/__tests__/waitlist-contract.test.ts` → 41/41 passed\n251\t  - Full unit suite (`vitest run --config vitest.unit.config.ts`) → 214/214 passed across 20 files\n252\t\n253\t## Iteration 11 — 2026-04-22T10:18:22Z — OK\n254\t- **Log**: iteration-011.log\n255\t\n256\t